80%9CThere%20were%20no%20limits%20to%20what%20we%20could%20create.%20We%20wanted%20to%20build%20something%20that%20would%20be%20genuinely%20useful%20to%20our%20families.%20Since%20both%20of%20our%20grandmothers%20had%20mobility%20issues%2C%20we%20focused%20on%20developing%20a%20solution%20for%20elders%20like%20them%20to%20help%20prevent%20falls.%20If%20we%20had%20known%20about%20her%20condition%20earlier%2C%20we%20might%20have%20been%20able%20to%20address%20it%20more%20effectively%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Hriday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20experiences%20ignited%20the%20students%E2%80%99%20desire%20to%20create%20a%20device%20that%20could%20offer%20early%20detection%20of%20mobility%20issues%2C%20potentially%20preventing%20severe%20health%20complications%20down%20the%20line.%20Intense%20brainstorming%20sessions%20followed%2C%20where%20wheelchairs%2C%20walking%20sticks%20and%20more%20were%20discussed.%20%E2%80%9CShould%20it%20be%20a%20foldable%20walking%20stick%2C%20a%20single%20cane%3F%E2%80%9D%20they%20thought.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20they%20focused%20on%20creating%20a%20stick%20that%20would%20analyse%20falls%20and%20provide%20a%20diagnosis.%20However%2C%20prohibitive%20costs%20forced%20them%20to%20rethink%20their%20approach.%20Since%20most%20seniors%20with%20gait%20issues%20already%20use%20a%20walking%20stick%2C%20they%20decided%20to%20develop%20a%20system%20that%20could%20be%20easily%20attached%20to%20any%20existing%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20product%20is%20a%20circuit%2C%20an%20attachment%20that%20can%20be%20fitted%20onto%20any%20stick%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rahi.%20They%20spent%20about%20three%20months%20on%20research%20and%20designing%20their%20circuit%20with%20the%20help%20of%20their%20mentors%20at%20Omotec.%20Over%20the%20next%20two%20years%2C%20they%20went%20through%20three%20prototypes%20and%20designs%20before%20coming%20up%20with%20their%20final%20retrofitted%20model%20in%20January%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20World%20Health%20Organisation%20(WHO)%20report%20states%20that%20falls%20are%20the%20second%20leading%20cause%20of%20unintentional%20injury%20deaths%20worldwide.%20It%20states%20that%20adults%20older%20than%2060%20years%20of%20age%20suffer%20the%20greatest%20number%20of%20fatal%20falls%20and%2037.3%20million%20falls%20every%20year%20require%20medical%20attention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20420px)%20100vw%2C%20420px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fheat-map-1724246900.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22420%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20circuit%20generates%20real-time%20heat%20maps%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fheat-map-1724246900.jpeg%20420w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fheat-map-1724246900-300x193.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fheat-map-1724246900-150x96.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-362428%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20circuit%20generates%20real-time%20heat%20maps%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWalkfit%20aims%20to%20be%20a%20preventive%20strategy%20for%20this%20massive%20problem.%20The%20duo%20worked%20with%20physiotherapists%20to%20understand%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F296115%2Fteenagers-startup-finance4teens-educate-kids-globally-on-banking-financial-literacy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebiomechanics%20of%20falls%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Meghavi%20Desai%20Bhuptani%2C%20one%20of%20the%20physiotherapists%20who%20helped%20the%20students%2C%20says%20that%20the%20device%20can%20be%20very%20helpful%20for%20people%20who%20lack%20stability.%20%E2%80%9COsteoarthritis%2C%20caused%20due%20to%20wear%20and%20tear%20of%2