tterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FKrop-AI-2-1723817299.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FKrop-AI-2-1723817299-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FKrop-AI-2-1723817299-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FKrop-AI-2-1723817299-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FKrop-AI-2-1723817299-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-361736%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ECalvin%20and%20Farish%20aimed%20to%20boost%20farmers%E2%80%99%20income%20and%20resilience%20against%20climate%20fluctuations.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarish%20continues%20to%20reiterate%20that%20Indian%20farmers%20are%20largely%20dependent%20on%20soil%2C%20water%2C%20and%20weather.%20%E2%80%9CWith%20rising%20input%20costs%20and%20poor%20yields%2C%20they%20incur%20huge%20losses%20and%20fall%20into%20subsequent%20debts.%20Hydroponics%20seemed%20a%20very%20good%20segment%20as%20it%20requires%2095%20percent%20less%20water%20and%20crops%20can%20be%20grown%20in%20a%20controlled%20environment%20with%20artificial%20light%20without%20depending%20on%20the%20weather%20outside%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Calvin%20points%20out%20that%20while%20groundwater%20is%20already%20depleting%20to%20severe%20levels%20and%20agricultural%20lands%20are%20decreasing%2C%20demand%20for%20food%20continues%20to%20increase.%20%E2%80%9CClimate%20change%20is%20rapid%20and%20crop%20loss%20will%20be%20substantial%20due%20to%20this.%20We%20understood%20that%20innovation%20in%20a%20controlled%20environment%20is%20crucial%20and%20AI%20will%20help%20us%20further%20our%20sustainable%20goals%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20weekend%2C%20Calvin%20and%20Farish%20spoke%20in%20detail%20on%20the%20persistent%20issue.%20With%20a%20shared%20passion%20for%20transforming%20the%20agricultural%20sector%20through%20technology-driven%20solutions%2C%20they%20eventually%20decided%20to%20completely%20shift%20their%20focus%20on%20making%20farming%20profitable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20Calvin%20quit%20his%20job%20and%20both%20friends%20rented%20a%20small%20flat%20in%20Udupi%20where%20they%20built%20a%20prototype%20using%20their%20pocket%20money.%20After%20four%20months%2C%20they%20started%20their%20company%2C%20Krop%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECutting%20operational%20costs%20to%20half%20with%20AI%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20offering%20container%20farm%20setups%20as%20an%20alternative%20to%20traditional%20polyhouse%20farming%2C%20Calvin%20and%20Farish%20aimed%20to%20boost%20farmers%E2%80%99%20income%20and%20resilience%20against%20climate%20fluctuations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FKrop-AI-1-1723817326.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Farish%20and%20Calvin%20are%20growing%20exotic%20crops%20such%20as%20lettuce%2C%20basil%2C%20kale%20and%20parsley%20using%20AI.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FKrop-AI-1-1723817326.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FKrop-AI-1-1723817326-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FKrop-AI-1-1723817326-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FKrop-AI-1-1723817326-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FKrop-AI-1-1723817326-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-361737%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EFarish%20and%20Calvin%20are%20growing%20exotic%20crops%20such%20as%20lettuce%2C%20basil%2C%20kale%20and%20parsley%20using%20AI.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20focussed%20on%20integrating%20advanced%20technology%20and%20automation%20to%20enhance%20crop%20quality%2C%20taste%2C%20and%20production%20efficiency%20while%20reducing%20operational%20costs.%20They%20built%20their%20own%203D%20pipes%20to%20grow%20crops%20vertically.%20%E2%80%9COur%20patented%20pipes%20allow%20precise%20control%20of%20environmental%20variables%20like%20light%20spectrum%20and%20temperature%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Farish.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20software%20inputs%2C%20the%20system%20irrigates%20and%20maintains%20temperature%2C%20humidity%2C%20pH%2C%20water%20conductivity%2C%20air%20temperature%2C%20humidity%2C%20and%20all%20other%20parameters%20to%20provide%20an%20ideal%20environment%20suitable%20for%20plant%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20used%20special%20spectrum%20lights%20that%20mimic%20sunlight%20but%20emit%20the%20exact%20wavelengths%20required%20for%20plant%20growth.%20An%20ideal%20plant%20requires%20light%20wavelengths%20between%20600%20and%20700%20nanometers%20for%20photosynthesis.%20For%20human%20eyes%2C%20they%20look%20purplish%20blue%20in%20colour%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Calvin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECompared%20to%20traditional%20farming%20methods%2C%20the%20AI-enabled%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F356971%2Fhydroponics-farming-without-soil-sustainable-agriculture-farmer-increases-income-solar-energy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehydroponic%20farming%20%3C%2Fa%3Emethod%20not%20only%20saves%2095%20percent%20of%20water%20as%20it%20is%20reused%20in%20the%20setup%20but%20also%20brings%20operational%20costs%20to%2050%20percent.%20This%2C%20Farish%20says%2C%20has%20the%20potential%20to