gs%20to%20furniture%20and%20bathroom%20accessories%2C%20elevators%2C%20wheelchairs%2C%20and%20emergency%20evacuation%20solutions.%20For%20instance%2C%20the%20team%20provides%20special%20wheelchairs%20that%20can%20navigate%20stairs%20during%20emergencies%20when%20elevators%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20used.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20sources%20these%20products%20from%20across%20India%2C%20both%20locally%20and%20centrally%2C%20to%20meet%20various%20needs.%20Through%20this%2C%20it%20has%20reinvigorated%20the%20industry%2C%20increasing%20supply%20and%20opening%20the%20market%20to%20new%20players%20focused%20on%20disability%20solutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99ve%20been%20asked%20by%20numerous%20organisations%20to%20create%20end-to-end%20accessibility%20solutions%20for%20their%20workplaces%2C%20which%20include%20everything%20from%20accessible%20parking%20and%20entry%20routes%20to%20doors%20and%20charging%20points.%20We%20also%20address%20how%20workspaces%2C%20card-punch%20areas%2C%20washrooms%2C%20and%20canteens%20are%20all%20designed%20to%20be%20inclusive%20and%20user-friendly%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEveryone%20talks%20about%20how%20India%20will%20be%20developed%20by%202047%2C%20but%20we%20must%20remember%20that%20true%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F216171%2Fips-hero-west-bengal-differently-abled-friendly-police-stations-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edevelopment%20starts%20with%20accessibility%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20Prateek%20shares%2C%20while%20remarking%20that%20countries%20like%20Singapore%20and%20those%20in%20Europe%20are%20considered%20developed%20because%20they%20are%20accessible.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20India%20to%20reach%20that%20level%2C%20accessibility%20must%20come%20first.%20This%20is%20the%20vision%20we%20strive%20for.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETapping%20into%20the%20corporate%20market%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20reality%20is%20that%20many%20people%20have%20limited%20budgets%20for%20accessibility%20features%2C%E2%80%9D%20states%20Prateek.%20Cafes%20might%20only%20spend%20a%20few%20thousand%20on%20ramps%2C%20but%20proper%20ramps%20with%20the%20right%20length%20and%20gradient%20cost%20more.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20the%20challenge%20for%20Prateek%20and%20his%20team%20because%20people%20wanted%20ramps%20but%20weren%E2%80%99t%20willing%20to%20pay%20for%20quality.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20needed%20to%20find%20a%20way%20to%20scale%20up%20quickly%2C%20aiming%20for%20thousands%20of%20ramps%20per%20year%2C%20not%20just%20dozens.%20Even%20large%20corporations%20with%20substantial%20revenues%20often%20don%E2%80%99t%20budget%20for%20true%20accessibility.%20We%20saw%20an%20opportunity%20in%20CSR%20and%20philanthropic%20funding%20to%20help%20us%20grow%20and%20meet%20our%20targets%2C%E2%80%9D%20Prateek%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20total%2C%2070%25%20of%20the%20total%20Corporate%20Social%20Responsibility%20(CSR)%20spending%20from%202018%20through%202021%20went%20to%20education%2C%20healthcare%2C%20rural%20development%2C%20environmental%20sustainability%2C%20and%20poverty%2C%20according%20to%20a%20Bain%20%26amp%3B%20Company%20report.%20RampMyCity%20approached%20these%20corporations%2C%20proposing%20they%20invest%20in%20public%20accessibility%20projects.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20offered%20to%20manage%20installations%20in%20public%20places%2C%20hospitals%2C%20and%20police%20stations%2C%20with%20the%20government%20providing%20the%20necessary%20permissions.%20This%20model%20has%20helped%20RampMyCity%20scale%20rapidly%2C%20shares%20Prateek%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20startup%20is%20currently%20working%20to%20tap%20into%20this%20large%20pool%20of%20CSR%20money%20to%20improve%20public%20infrastructure.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20how%20he%20stayed%20motivated%20during%20the%20early%20days%20of%20his%20startup%20while%20adjusting%20to%20life%20in%20a%20wheelchair%20and%20an%20unclear%20path%20ahead%2C%20Prateek%20says%20it%20was%20all%20about%20taking%20baby%20steps.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20you%20are%20consistent%20in%20working%20towards%20your%20goals%2C%20there%20will%20always%20be%20a%20way%20forward%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares%2C%20quoting%20his%20personal%20mantra%3A%20%3Cem%3EKismat%20ke%20bharose%20mat%20baithiye%3B%20kismat%20khud%20aapke%20bharose%20baithi%20hai%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Don%E2%80%99t%20wait%20for%20luck%2Fkismet%3B%20it%20is%20waiting%20for%20you%20to%20make%20a%20move).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20injury%20forced%20me%20to%20face%20myself.%20I%20could%20either%20become%20my%20greatest%20ally%20or%20my%20biggest%20enemy%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%20Years%20after%20the%20accident%2C%20when%20Prateek%20reviewed%20his%20life%2C%20his%20past%20achievements%2C%20and%20took%20note%20of%20the%20go-getting%20attitude%20he%20had%20always%20had%2C%20he%20was%20able%20to%20piece%20together%20his%20identity.%20This%20led%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F288588%2Fbrittle-bone-disease-didnt-stop-kerala-doctor-fathima-asla-inspiration%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erenewed%20focus%20on%20his%20goals%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20those%20facing%20similar%20struggles%2C%20his%20advice%20is%20to%20trust%20the%20process.%20%E2%80%9COver%20time%2C%20you%20will%20see%20how%20the%20bigger%20plan%20was%20made%20for%20you.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ve%20never%20regretted%20my%20injury%20or%20my%20life%20in%20a%20wheelchair.%20Instead%2C%20I%20see%20it%20as%20an%20amazing%20opportunity%20that%20I%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20had%20otherwise.%20It%E2%80%99s%20allowed%20me%20to%20see%20how%20many%20people%20with%20disabilities%20can%20live%20full%2C%20normal%20lives%3B%20travel%2C%20work%2C%20and%20be%20part%20of%20society.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20Pictures%20Courtesy%3A%20Prateek%20Khandelwal%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3ESources%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bain.com%2Fglobalassets%2Fnoindex%2F2022%2Fbain_report_india_philanthropy_report-2022.pdf%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.bain.com%2Fglobalassets%2Fnoindex%2F2022%2Fbain_report_india_philanthropy_report-2022.pdf%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Bain%20%26amp%3B%20Company%20India%20Philanthrophy%20Report%202022%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldbank.org%2Fen%2Ftopic%2Fdisability%23%3A~%3Atext%3DOne%2520billion%2520people%252C%2520or%252015%2Cexperience%2520some%2520form%2520of%2520disability.%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldbank.org%2Fen%2Ftopic%2Fdisability%23%3A~%3Atext%3DOne%2520billion%2520people%252C%2520or%252015%2Cexperience%2520some%2520form%2520of%2520disability.%3C%2Fa%3E%20Disability%20Inclusion%20%E2%80%93%20World%20Bank%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiacode.nic.in%2Fbitstream%2F123456789%2F15939%2F1%2Fthe_rights_of_persons_with_disabilities_act%252C_2016.pdf%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiacode.nic.in%2Fbitstream%2F123456789%2F15939%2F1%2Fthe_rights_of_persons_with_disabilities_act%252C_2016.pdf%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20Rights%20Of%20Persons%20With%20Disabilities%20Act%2C%202016%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723821866000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-27_11zon-1723818970.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D361727%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bengaluru-based%20Prateek%20Khandelwal%20was%20paralysed%20after%20an%20accident.%20As%20a%20wheelchair-user%2C%20he%20feared%20that%20he%20would%20be%20forced%20into%20a%20permanent%20lockdown.%20He%20started%20RampMyCity%2C%20a%20startup%20working%20towards%20making%20public%20places%20inclusive%20and%20disabled-friendly.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tanvi%20Dalvi%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F361727%2Fwheelchair-friendly-places-to-visit-in-bengaluru-ramp-my-city-prateek-khandelwal-access-for-disabled-people%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%202%20Friends%20Built%20Low-Cost%2C%20Eco-Toilets%20in%20a%20Rural%20Govt%20School%20in%20Just%201%20Month%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EJust%20a%20while%20ago%2C%20students%20in%20the%20government%20school%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%E2%80%99s%20Nellivasal%20village%20were%20forced%20to%20go%20out%20in%20the%20open%20for%20defecation.%20Without%20any%20proper%20toilet%20facility%2C%20they%20urinated%20at%20the%20corner%20of%20the%20campus%20building%20at%20night%2C%20creating%20a%20stench%20in%20the%20entire%20hostel%20block%20that%20made%20it%20unbearable%20to%20sit%20in%20the%20dining%20area%20of%20the%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocated%20in%20the%20hilly%20forest%20area%20of%20the%20Jawadhu%20Hills%20(Eastern%20Ghats)%20in%20Tirupathur%20district%2C%20the%20tribal%20village%20school%20lacked%20toilet%20facilities%2C%20owing%20to%20its%20remote%20location%20and%20financial%20constraints.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20continued%20until%20architect%20Barnala%20Michael%2C%20architect-turned-documentary%20filmmaker%20Vishnupriya%2C%20and%20a%20group%20of%20like-minded%20friends%20came%20together%20to%20solve%20the%20social%20issue%20through%20collective%20effort%20and%20crowdfunding.%20Keeping%20the%20constraints%20in%20mind%2C%20they%20adopted%20an%20unconventional%20design%20approach%20with%20unique%20toilet%20units%20and%20cost-effective%20construction%20methods%20and%20techniques.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20they%20constructed%20three%20toilets%20and%20an%20open%20bath%20area%20that%20cost%20Rs%202.5%20lakh%20%E2%80%94%2